[38;2;192;202;245m[48;2;26;27;38m  Synthesizes via /v1/t2a_v2, lists system voices via /v1/get_voice,           [39m[49m                                         
[38;2;192;202;245m[48;2;26;27;38m  transcodes MP3 to opus for voice-note targets.                               [39m[49m                                         
